data.description: NEW PRICE!!! Wonderfully cared for, one-owner home on the greenbelt in the awesome community of Sendera Ranch. Residents enjoy multiple swimming pools, catch and release ponds, trails, playgrounds, and sport courts.  This like-new, efficient and open floorpan has split bedrooms, a large and open living area attached to the kitchen and dining room.  The living room has been updated with decorative shiplap wallpaper on one wall which is a great focal point.  All living areas have luxury vinyl plank flooring which is easy to maintain. The backyard has amazing views of the greenbelt and pastures behind the home. Energy efficient and easy to maintain, you'll find this a great place to call home!  Students attend Northwest ISD schools - JC Thompson, Wilson Middle & Northwest High School.  Easy access out of the community via John Day Road.  All information to be verified by buyer.
